1.0.name: wordpress/levelfourstorefront
1.0.description:
The WordPress L4 shopping cart system is now located under a new name of WP EasyCart. You can view it by searching for WP EasyCart from anywhere in the WordPress plugin system.

  • Click Here to visit our website

  • Click Here to visit our new plugin page

We are also providing a full service website loaded with new features in this release. Online documentation systems, video tutorial library, plus online community forums so you can get help to questions you have.

You can also view our website at http://www.wpeasycart.com for more information.
